2010-08-20  J.W. Janssen <j.w.janssen@lxtreme.nl>

	*
	device.logicsniffer/src/main/java/org/sump/device/logicsniffer/Logi
	cSnifferConfigDialog.java,
	util/src/main/java/nl/lxtreme/ols/util/DisplayUtils.java: Added a
	warning when the number of channel groups outlimits the capture
	size; added an option to automatically select the capture size based
	on the selected channel groups.

